snippet.title: Amber Heard as Mera, Punisher on Netflix, and Deadpool 2 - Geek Out For A Minute
snippet.description:
Today we got a full panel when Boone, Cyrus, Jack Platinum and Rocky Ruiz go over Amber Heard's first look as Mera for the upcoming Justice League and Aquaman. Also as Ben Barnes joins the cast of Marvel/Netflix Punisher series and Deadpool 2 short list to cast Domino, also Tim Miller leaves the project due to creative differences.

If your in the area come to the bar and hang out with us.
